Sarkozy Says He Has Confidence in Italian Authorities ‘Overall’

-- B y   H e l e n e   F o u q u e t
-- 
2011-10-23T15:15:03Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-23/sarkozy-says-he-has-confidence-in-italian-authorities-overall-.html
President  Nicolas Sarkozy  said he
has confidence in the Italian authorities “overall.”  “Let’s trust the sense of responsibility of the Italian
authorities as a whole,” Sarkozy said at a press conference in
Brussels.  To contact the reporter on this story:
